OL,3,CCould 75,000 train ticket fines be
OL,4,Coverturned in landmark case?
OL,6,FChristian refused to pay the #20 fine.
OL,7,FHe planned to appeal and assumed if
OL,8,Fthat was unsuccessful he'd be taken to
OL,9,Fa civil court.
OL,11,FBut Northern, in line with other train
OL,12,Fcompanies, used a fast-track
OL,13,Fprosecution known as a Single Justice
OL,14,FProcedure or SJP which allows a
OL,15,Fmagistrates' hearing to be held behind
OL,16,Fclosed doors.
OL,18,FNorthern says it has since stopped
OL,19,Fusing SJPs in fare evasion cases.
