OL,6,FA Northern spokesperson said: "There
OL,7,Fare multiple ways to buy a Northern
OL,8,Ftrain ticket including on the app, our
OL,9,Fwebsite, from ticket vending machines
OL,10,For ticket offices - and our colleagues
OL,11,Fare happy to provide advice if needed.
OL,12,FWe remind people of the need to buy
OL,13,Ftickets at stations and on trains.
OL,15,F"Our focus remains on ensuring that
OL,16,Fall our customers are treated fairly,
OL,17,Fwhich means ensuring all passengers
OL,18,Fwho board our trains have a valid
OL,19,Fticket.
